form.official-title: To deauthorize portions of the project for raising and improving existing levees on the Walluski River in Clatsop County, Oregon.

section.header: Deauthorization of levee project on Walluski River in Clatsop County, Oregon
section.text: The portions of the project for raising and improving existing levees of Clatsop County Diking District No. 13 in Clatsop County, Oregon, authorized by section 5 of the Act of June 22, 1936 (49 Stat. 1590), that are referred to as Christensen No. 1 Dike No. 42 and Christensen No. 2 Levee No. 43 are no longer authorized beginning on the date of enactment of this Act.
